parameters.name: AddressFamily
parameters.description:
The IP address family of the prefix list. Valid values:

*   IPv4
*   IPv6

This parameter is empty by default, which indicates that all prefix lists are queried.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
The number of entries to return on each page.

Maximum value: 100.

Default value: 10.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The query token. Set the value to the `NextToken` value returned in the previous call to the DescribePrefixLists operation. Leave this parameter empty the first time you call this operation.

parameters.name: PrefixListName
parameters.description: The name of the prefix list.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
